body_html: One thing which i want to ask is this , i am using tensorflow inference on android , now i have been using two ops tf.nn.dilation and tf.nn.erosion in my training , and while inference it says no op kernel was registered for this , now is it possible that tensorflow inference on android is not able to understand these ops even though these ops were working on tensorflow GPU?
